divs: Sighting DetailsI was posing down on some rocks having some pictures taken of my stylish posing self. Myself and my company didn't see the objects in the sky until we were viewing a slide show of the pictures that evening. In one picture there are 2 objects, and in the next, (taken a few seconds later) there are 4 objects...
